&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bring the web platform to the table, not just the design spec.&lt;/strong&gt; You’ll surface what’s newly possible in browsers, propose enhancements that design didn’t know to ask for, and advocate for approaches that make experiences feel alive rather than translated from a static file.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Implement animation and interaction that earns attention.&lt;/strong&gt; Product launches, campaign pages, and editorial moments require more than accurate layouts. They require pacing, motion, and detail; you’ll own that layer.&lt;/li&gt;
