&lt;li&gt;Hire, mentor, and retain high-performing engineers across experience levels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help shape the organization structure as the payment rails group scales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coach emerging leaders within the group&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive predictable execution against company and product goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a healthy, engaging, and high-performing team environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uphold a high bar for technical quality, reliability, and system stability&lt;/li&gt;
