&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with product and design to identify and prioritize high-impact work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate across teams to build cohesive products and simpler, more maintainable systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Balance new development with ongoing maintenance and operational excellence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
